Brooklyn is a borough in New York City; 
Neighbourhood groups refer to broader geographic areas within the borough, such as Downtown Brooklyn or Brooklyn Heights; 
Reviews and bookings are measures of a property's popularity and usage, which can help inform pricing decisions and neighbourhood comparisons.

